# Description

This pull request adds a new feature that enables users to filter search results by category. This enhancement is part of our ongoing effort to improve search relevance and user experience.

- **Context:**  
  Our product requirements and recent user feedback indicated the need for advanced filtering options. This change aligns with our planned roadmap for search improvements and supports the new UI designs scheduled for the next release.

- **Motivation:**  
  Adding filtering functionality will help users quickly narrow down search results, reduce time-to-find, and improve overall engagement on our platform.

